Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

IMAPAccount personal
Host imap.fastmail.com
User willfleming@fastmail.fm
PassCmd "pass fastmail.com/imap"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore personal-remote
Account personal

MaildirStore personal-local
Path ~/mail/personal/
Inbox ~/mail/personal/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel personal
Master :personal-remote:
Slave :personal-local:
Patterns * !Notes

IMAPAccount codeclimate
Host imap.gmail.com
User will@codeclimate.com
PassCmd "pass cc/imap"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore codeclimate-remote
Account codeclimate

MaildirStore codeclimate-local
Path ~/mail/codeclimate/
Inbox ~/mail/codeclimate/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel codeclimate
Master :codeclimate-remote:
Slave :codeclimate-local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Starred" "[Gmail]/All Mail" "[Gmail]/Trash"
